description:
PLEASE FORGIVE ANY ISSUES, I'M NEW TO UPLOADING.


******* I'm doing a test run with different court shows, to see which court shows people want to download, besides the ever popular ones. If anyone has a specific request, comment and I'll do my best to find what I can. ---Bear with me on file sizes or quality- I'll eventually get it down pat, but at the moment, I have no idea what I'm doing :)





Since us court show fanatics are missing our uploads from "The People's Court" (who I'm sure are busy right now and will be back), I'm trying to find as many episodes of The Peoples Court and JJ as I can and I'll try to upload them. 



*****I only have regular upload speeds of around 300-400kB, so please forgive slow speeds. Thank you to all the people who've said thanks, and the people seeding! I really appreciate it
